1
00:00:19,900 --> 00:00:24,380
(Mingguang Temple)

2
00:01:23,640 --> 00:01:25,150
(Bai Zhi, Believer of Mingguang Temple)
I, Bai Zhi,

3
00:01:25,510 --> 00:01:27,430
have come to pray for Buddha's blessing.

4
00:01:28,070 --> 00:01:30,480
May my husband live in peace and joy.

5
00:01:31,040 --> 00:01:33,710
I will honor Buddha's teachings,

6
00:01:33,870 --> 00:01:35,150
do good deeds,

7
00:01:35,200 --> 00:01:37,511
uphold the precepts,
and chant the scriptures faithfully.

8
00:01:42,500 --> 00:01:48,980
=The Tang Mist S1=

9
00:03:07,620 --> 00:03:09,620
=Episode 21=

10
00:03:21,800 --> 00:03:24,030
(Why fear death
if we are paired like the flouders?)

11
00:03:24,400 --> 00:03:26,560
(I'd rather be a pair of lovebirds
than an immortal.)

12
00:03:31,400 --> 00:03:34,150
(The old sachet is gone,
so do not dwell on it anymore.)

13
00:03:34,590 --> 00:03:36,710
(I prepared this new pouch for you.)

14
00:03:37,960 --> 00:03:40,190
(May it gladden your heart
when you see it,)

15
00:03:41,030 --> 00:03:42,520
(and smooth away your frown)

16
00:03:42,800 --> 00:03:44,310
(with joy.)

17
00:03:55,430 --> 00:03:57,000
What are those people doing?

18
00:04:00,130 --> 00:04:00,960
A coffin?

19
00:04:01,680 --> 00:04:03,030
Looks like a burial.

20
00:04:04,000 --> 00:04:05,150
There's no mourning banner,

21
00:04:05,630 --> 00:04:06,750
and no one's crying.

22
00:04:06,750 --> 00:04:08,460
The constables are there, too.

23
00:04:08,560 --> 00:04:09,800
Could something have happened?

24
00:04:10,430 --> 00:04:10,910
Duan,

25
00:04:11,310 --> 00:04:12,000
go take a look.

26
00:04:12,030 --> 00:04:13,190
Show some respect.

27
00:04:15,177 --> 00:04:16,040
That's enough.

28
00:04:16,310 --> 00:04:17,070
Stop crying.

29
00:04:18,530 --> 00:04:19,750
Hurry up and get moving.

30
00:04:20,050 --> 00:04:21,000
Work faster.

31
00:04:22,160 --> 00:04:23,910
What are you doing here?

32
00:04:25,600 --> 00:04:26,870
Who are you?

33
00:04:27,040 --> 00:04:27,800
Move along.

34
00:04:28,340 --> 00:04:29,930
The Imperial Commissioner of Jiangnan,

35
00:04:30,470 --> 00:04:31,890
Di Renjie,

36
00:04:34,480 --> 00:04:35,430
is here.

37
00:04:38,120 --> 00:04:38,870
Commissioner Di.

38
00:04:38,870 --> 00:04:40,800
This is not a common grave.

39
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:43,190
Why is the body being buried here?

40
00:04:43,200 --> 00:04:45,990
Sir, the south of the city is under
construction, so the road is blocked.

41
00:04:46,000 --> 00:04:48,510
This place was designated
as a new burial ground.

42
00:04:55,480 --> 00:04:57,040
Who is being buried?

43
00:04:57,040 --> 00:04:58,070
What happened?

44
00:04:59,600 --> 00:05:01,360
This is my daughter, Lian.

45
00:05:01,360 --> 00:05:02,830
She was murdered

46
00:05:03,070 --> 00:05:04,560
and died an unjust death.

47
00:05:05,160 --> 00:05:06,630
Prefect Sun specially approved

48
00:05:07,180 --> 00:05:09,070
her burial

49
00:05:09,120 --> 00:05:10,270
so she could rest in peace.

50
00:05:10,270 --> 00:05:11,310
Specially approved?

51
00:05:13,066 --> 00:05:14,577
The case hasn't been solved yet?

52
00:05:15,360 --> 00:05:16,110
Sir,

53
00:05:16,620 --> 00:05:17,360
the case

54
00:05:17,830 --> 00:05:18,560
can't be solved.

55
00:05:19,240 --> 00:05:20,040
This is ridiculous!

56
00:05:20,355 --> 00:05:22,780
The case remains unsolved,
and the murderer is still at large.

57
00:05:22,800 --> 00:05:23,830
Why permit the burial?

58
00:05:24,160 --> 00:05:24,870
Sir,

59
00:05:25,270 --> 00:05:26,830
the murder

60
00:05:26,830 --> 00:05:28,000
was gruesome.

61
00:05:28,100 --> 00:05:29,510
The body had begun to rot and smell.

62
00:05:29,510 --> 00:05:30,870
The situation was extremely unusual.

63
00:05:30,880 --> 00:05:33,390
I was worried
it would cause panic among the people,

64
00:05:33,500 --> 00:05:34,190
so I...

65
00:05:34,600 --> 00:05:35,510
Unusual?

66
00:05:36,720 --> 00:05:37,630
Open the coffin.

67
00:05:55,360 --> 00:05:56,240
Sir,

68
00:05:56,460 --> 00:05:57,240
Lian's body

69
00:05:57,380 --> 00:05:58,590
was buried earlier today.

70
00:05:58,688 --> 00:06:00,080
But not far from Mingguang Temple,

71
00:06:00,200 --> 00:06:02,511
(Wu Yueze, Magistrate of Xin'an County)
there's another female corpse in red.

72
00:06:02,555 --> 00:06:03,600
(Sun Mao, Prefect of Quzhou)

73
00:06:03,600 --> 00:06:06,190
This makes the third victim
within half a month.

74
00:06:08,240 --> 00:06:09,330
Keep this quiet.

75
00:06:09,450 --> 00:06:10,610
Do not spread panic.

76
00:06:11,120 --> 00:06:12,080
Find out who she is.

77
00:06:13,180 --> 00:06:15,400
I'll personally console the family.

78
00:06:15,400 --> 00:06:16,020
Yes, sir.

79
00:06:18,380 --> 00:06:20,540
The previous body
hasn't finished examination,

80
00:06:20,622 --> 00:06:21,930
and now there's another one.

81
00:06:22,580 --> 00:06:24,540
There's no end to the turmoil
in Xin'an County.

82
00:06:27,660 --> 00:06:29,100
The fatal injuries on both corpses

83
00:06:29,100 --> 00:06:30,240
were broken necks.

84
00:06:30,810 --> 00:06:32,240
Aside from the severed tongues

85
00:06:32,340 --> 00:06:34,060
and wounds around the eyes and mouth,

86
00:06:34,310 --> 00:06:35,570
there were no other injuries.

87
00:06:37,260 --> 00:06:38,380
Neither lady

88
00:06:38,710 --> 00:06:39,900
was assaulted.

89
00:06:41,450 --> 00:06:42,240
Sir,

90
00:06:42,550 --> 00:06:44,000
this is the third murder case.

91
00:06:44,780 --> 00:06:45,590
Half a month ago,

92
00:06:46,070 --> 00:06:48,933
the first victim, Lady Gui,
was discovered on a forest path.

93
00:06:49,250 --> 00:06:50,540
About seven days ago,

94
00:06:50,810 --> 00:06:52,660
the second victim, Lian,
was found beside

95
00:06:52,740 --> 00:06:54,660
a small river near
the previous crime scene.

96
00:06:54,840 --> 00:06:55,740
And today,

97
00:06:55,890 --> 00:06:57,740
the third victim, Yanzhi, was found.

98
00:06:57,850 --> 00:06:58,710
All three victims

99
00:06:58,970 --> 00:07:00,310
were killed on rainy days.

100
00:07:01,120 --> 00:07:02,320
There's one strange detail.

101
00:07:02,780 --> 00:07:04,060
Lady Gui and Yanzhi

102
00:07:04,260 --> 00:07:05,680
both had their tongues removed.

103
00:07:06,050 --> 00:07:08,340
Only Lian had not only
her eyes gouged out,

104
00:07:09,010 --> 00:07:10,400
but her mouth sewn shut as well.

105
00:07:11,480 --> 00:07:14,070
Where is the first victim's body?

106
00:07:14,266 --> 00:07:15,580
It's already been half a month.

107
00:07:15,580 --> 00:07:16,700
The body started to smell,

108
00:07:17,100 --> 00:07:18,340
so she was buried.

109
00:07:18,350 --> 00:07:19,980
But the coroner examined
everything carefully

110
00:07:19,980 --> 00:07:20,780
and recorded it all.

111
00:07:21,020 --> 00:07:21,860
Prefect Sun

112
00:07:22,260 --> 00:07:23,700
also visited the victim's families.

113
00:07:23,844 --> 00:07:25,020
Where are the case files?

114
00:07:26,700 --> 00:07:27,500
The case files

115
00:07:29,100 --> 00:07:29,900
are missing.

116
00:07:29,940 --> 00:07:31,220
How could they disappear?

117
00:07:31,540 --> 00:07:32,460
Go find them.

118
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:34,100
Go ahead.

119
00:07:34,270 --> 00:07:34,820
Yes, sir.

120
00:07:39,790 --> 00:07:41,380
Judging by the methods used,

121
00:07:42,060 --> 00:07:43,860
these appear to be revenge killings.

122
00:07:45,260 --> 00:07:47,580
All three victims wore red.

123
00:07:47,580 --> 00:07:48,740
That cannot be a coincidence.

124
00:07:49,830 --> 00:07:51,820
What does the red clothing represent?

125
00:07:52,700 --> 00:07:55,460
What kind of obsession
is the killer venting?

126
00:07:56,860 --> 00:07:57,900
Magistrate Wu,

127
00:07:58,333 --> 00:08:00,200
investigate the source
of the red garments.

128
00:08:00,288 --> 00:08:01,620
See if anything unusual turns up.

129
00:08:01,630 --> 00:08:04,060
Issue an order. The sale of red clothing
is forbidden throughout the city.

130
00:08:04,060 --> 00:08:05,660
Post notices everywhere
and inform the people

131
00:08:05,660 --> 00:08:07,860
not to wear red outdoors
for the time being.

132
00:08:07,860 --> 00:08:08,660
Yes, sir.

133
00:08:16,540 --> 00:08:19,260
Had Lian been in contact
with anyone lately?

134
00:08:19,460 --> 00:08:20,460
Anything unusual?

135
00:08:21,700 --> 00:08:24,260
Lian was a quiet person.

136
00:08:25,020 --> 00:08:26,460
She rarely interacted with others.

137
00:08:27,780 --> 00:08:29,180
But over the past month,

138
00:08:29,180 --> 00:08:30,580
she seemed distracted

139
00:08:30,620 --> 00:08:32,180
and often had nightmares.

140
00:08:32,340 --> 00:08:33,740
So she often

141
00:08:33,980 --> 00:08:36,020
went to Mingguang Temple

142
00:08:36,600 --> 00:08:37,780
to pray.

143
00:08:39,780 --> 00:08:41,500
Did anything happen to her?

144
00:08:45,620 --> 00:08:46,780
No.

145
00:08:49,500 --> 00:08:50,660
The dead is gone.

146
00:08:51,022 --> 00:08:52,180
I'm sorry for your loss.

147
00:08:54,140 --> 00:08:55,140
Thank you, sir.

148
00:08:57,860 --> 00:08:59,600
(Yafang Pavilion)
People are terrified now.

149
00:08:59,610 --> 00:09:01,860
(Sales of Red Garments Suspended)
The shop has stopped selling red clothing.

150
00:09:01,860 --> 00:09:03,020
Rest assured, sir.

151
00:09:04,060 --> 00:09:04,940
Well done.

152
00:09:05,850 --> 00:09:07,560
Many women in red have died lately.

153
00:09:07,560 --> 00:09:08,260
Take care, sir.

154
00:09:08,260 --> 00:09:09,260
This is getting eerie.

155
00:09:09,740 --> 00:09:10,900
Look at Magistrate Wu.

156
00:09:11,140 --> 00:09:12,580
His face is as pale as paper.

157
00:09:12,580 --> 00:09:14,380
He probably hasn't slept a wink.

158
00:09:14,740 --> 00:09:16,620
Why is the rouge store closed?

159
00:09:16,822 --> 00:09:18,600
Where are we supposed to buy rouge now?

160
00:09:18,620 --> 00:09:19,420
Tell me about it.

161
00:09:19,980 --> 00:09:21,020
It was open just yesterday.

162
00:09:21,030 --> 00:09:21,820
Such a waste of good rouge.

163
00:09:21,820 --> 00:09:23,300
(Rouge Store)
Four lovely ladies!

164
00:09:26,460 --> 00:09:27,940
What rouge are you talking about?

165
00:09:27,950 --> 00:09:30,460
The rouge from Rouge Store, of course.
They're of fine quality.

166
00:09:30,740 --> 00:09:31,820
Now that the shop is closed,

167
00:09:31,820 --> 00:09:33,700
we have nowhere to buy rouge.

168
00:09:33,700 --> 00:09:34,980
Why did it close?

169
00:09:34,980 --> 00:09:36,780
The owner of the shop,

170
00:09:36,780 --> 00:09:37,820
Yanzhi,

171
00:09:37,980 --> 00:09:39,140
was murdered.

172
00:09:39,140 --> 00:09:41,500
Why was she killed?

173
00:09:41,660 --> 00:09:43,420
Yanzhi always thought
too highly of herself.

174
00:09:43,820 --> 00:09:44,820
No man was good enough

175
00:09:44,820 --> 00:09:45,660
to catch her eye.

176
00:09:45,660 --> 00:09:46,700
She held out so long

177
00:09:46,740 --> 00:09:47,980
that she became an old spinster.

178
00:09:48,330 --> 00:09:49,060
In fact,

179
00:09:49,220 --> 00:09:50,700
she was flirtatious and always

180
00:09:50,755 --> 00:09:52,511
fooling around with one man
after another.

181
00:09:52,644 --> 00:09:54,660
Who knows whom she offended?

182
00:09:54,700 --> 00:09:55,520
I noticed

183
00:09:55,520 --> 00:09:56,720
she'd been going

184
00:09:56,720 --> 00:09:57,980
to Mingguang Temple often.

185
00:09:58,060 --> 00:10:00,570
Maybe she was praying
for a nice marriage.

186
00:10:01,260 --> 00:10:02,580
You four beauties

187
00:10:02,580 --> 00:10:03,690
really are observant

188
00:10:03,700 --> 00:10:04,990
and well-informed.

189
00:10:08,140 --> 00:10:09,380
Everyone in Xin'an City

190
00:10:09,380 --> 00:10:10,820
knows us.

191
00:10:10,820 --> 00:10:11,780
Xiazhu.

192
00:10:11,780 --> 00:10:12,660
Chunhua.

193
00:10:12,660 --> 00:10:13,820
Qiulan.

194
00:10:13,820 --> 00:10:14,980
Dongju.

195
00:10:15,200 --> 00:10:17,420
- We're the Four Golden Flowers.
- Four Golden Flowers.

196
00:10:21,580 --> 00:10:22,420
Merciful Buddha,

197
00:10:23,380 --> 00:10:24,220
what a sin...

198
00:10:24,420 --> 00:10:25,260
Enough chatter.

199
00:10:25,300 --> 00:10:25,860
Look!

200
00:10:25,860 --> 00:10:26,900
Beauty is out!

201
00:10:28,780 --> 00:10:29,540
Really?

202
00:10:33,340 --> 00:10:35,940
(Sales of Red Garments Suspended)

203
00:10:36,620 --> 00:10:38,780
General Wang Zhong is back!

204
00:10:43,660 --> 00:10:45,820
I heard General Wang fought bravely
on the frontier,

205
00:10:45,820 --> 00:10:47,100
leading the charge himself

206
00:10:47,100 --> 00:10:49,220
and crushing the enemy completely.

207
00:10:49,711 --> 00:10:50,700
Now that we've seen him,

208
00:10:50,700 --> 00:10:52,100
not only is he capable, but he's

209
00:10:52,100 --> 00:10:53,880
(Wang Zhong, Frontier General)
also handsome too.

210
00:10:53,980 --> 00:10:54,900
Exactly.

211
00:10:54,900 --> 00:10:56,020
With him protecting us,

212
00:10:56,020 --> 00:10:57,500
we can sleep peacefully at night.

213
00:11:00,480 --> 00:11:02,500
I wonder which lucky lady

214
00:11:02,500 --> 00:11:05,460
will marry such a fine man.

215
00:11:13,770 --> 00:11:14,750
Four years ago,

216
00:11:14,890 --> 00:11:17,140
Bai Zhi and Wang Zhong
fell in love at first sight.

217
00:11:17,140 --> 00:11:18,820
It was truly a celebrated love story.

218
00:11:19,020 --> 00:11:20,700
Yanzhi was there, too.

219
00:11:20,700 --> 00:11:22,100
She was so jealous.

220
00:11:22,140 --> 00:11:24,540
She said if she'd been the one
wearing that red dress,

221
00:11:24,540 --> 00:11:25,860
Wang Zhong would've

222
00:11:25,860 --> 00:11:26,940
fallen for her instead.

223
00:11:27,100 --> 00:11:28,620
Yanzhi and Wang Zhong?

224
00:11:30,020 --> 00:11:30,860
How could Wang Zhong

225
00:11:31,180 --> 00:11:32,500
possibly like her?

226
00:11:32,540 --> 00:11:33,140
Right?

227
00:11:33,430 --> 00:11:35,380
But after that, she started wearing red

228
00:11:35,580 --> 00:11:36,820
like Bai Zhi did.

229
00:11:37,180 --> 00:11:39,980
Yet I haven't seen Bai Zhi wear red

230
00:11:39,980 --> 00:11:41,380
for quite some time.

231
00:11:41,980 --> 00:11:44,380
She wears red dress constantly?

232
00:11:44,380 --> 00:11:45,590
That red dress

233
00:11:45,610 --> 00:11:47,020
came from the clothing shop

234
00:11:47,020 --> 00:11:48,700
owned by the richest merchant, He Xun.

235
00:11:49,220 --> 00:11:50,940
He's Bai Zhi's godfather.

236
00:11:50,980 --> 00:11:52,540
To attract customers,

237
00:11:52,540 --> 00:11:54,260
Bai Zhi has worn
those dresses for years.

238
00:11:54,420 --> 00:11:56,660
That's why she earns the nickname
"Beauty in Red".

239
00:11:56,980 --> 00:11:57,420
See,

240
00:11:57,420 --> 00:11:59,540
Wang Zhong had been back for two years.

241
00:11:59,900 --> 00:12:01,300
They loved each other deeply.

242
00:12:01,300 --> 00:12:02,900
Why haven't they had a child yet?

243
00:12:04,460 --> 00:12:06,380
Maybe Bai Zhi can't bear children.

244
00:12:06,780 --> 00:12:07,500
That's possible.

245
00:12:07,500 --> 00:12:09,620
We're not finished yet. Don't go.

246
00:12:10,980 --> 00:12:12,260
Four lovely ladies,

247
00:12:12,780 --> 00:12:14,140
if you discover anything else,

248
00:12:14,140 --> 00:12:16,020
please report it to the Bureau.

249
00:12:19,660 --> 00:12:20,660
Oh, this little fellow

250
00:12:20,660 --> 00:12:21,860
is actually an officer.

251
00:12:22,500 --> 00:12:23,020
Officer,

252
00:12:23,020 --> 00:12:24,420
don't you worry.

253
00:12:24,620 --> 00:12:26,260
Nothing that happens in this city

254
00:12:26,260 --> 00:12:29,180
escapes our discerning eyes.

255
00:12:32,060 --> 00:12:33,460
The body has been buried.

256
00:12:33,740 --> 00:12:34,980
The case files are missing.

257
00:12:35,300 --> 00:12:37,044
How exactly do you plan
to solve this case

258
00:12:37,180 --> 00:12:38,580
and catch the killer?

259
00:12:38,820 --> 00:12:39,940
Please forgive me.

260
00:12:40,260 --> 00:12:41,300
Di,

261
00:12:41,420 --> 00:12:44,060
the red garments all came
from the richest merchant, He Xun.

262
00:12:44,060 --> 00:12:46,100
They're sold in several shops.

263
00:12:46,100 --> 00:12:47,940
Nothing seemed unusual there.

264
00:12:47,940 --> 00:12:49,260
I also found out

265
00:12:49,260 --> 00:12:51,620
that Yanzhi frequented

266
00:12:51,840 --> 00:12:52,940
Mingguang Temple.

267
00:12:53,260 --> 00:12:53,980
Sir,

268
00:12:54,340 --> 00:12:55,580
according to the coroner,

269
00:12:55,740 --> 00:12:56,780
the first victim, Lady Gui,

270
00:12:56,780 --> 00:12:58,020
also died from a broken neck.

271
00:12:58,020 --> 00:12:59,580
There were no other injuries.

272
00:12:59,860 --> 00:13:00,700
Her body

273
00:13:00,920 --> 00:13:03,420
was also found in the bushes
below Mingguang Temple.

274
00:13:03,770 --> 00:13:05,020
Mingguang Temple again?

275
00:13:05,577 --> 00:13:07,844
Before Lian died,
she also visited Mingguang Temple often.

276
00:13:08,060 --> 00:13:09,740
So she visited

277
00:13:09,740 --> 00:13:10,820
Mingguang Temple often

278
00:13:11,410 --> 00:13:12,360
to pray.

279
00:13:12,740 --> 00:13:14,260
Where is Mingguang Temple?

280
00:13:14,660 --> 00:13:15,780
Anything unusual there?

281
00:13:16,060 --> 00:13:16,900
Sir,

282
00:13:16,900 --> 00:13:18,260
it's halfway up West Mountain.

283
00:13:18,311 --> 00:13:20,260
The temple was built
during the late Northern Wei period.

284
00:13:20,260 --> 00:13:21,940
The current abbot's Dharma name is Huiwu.

285
00:13:21,940 --> 00:13:23,820
He's highly respected
and skilled in medicine.

286
00:13:23,820 --> 00:13:25,780
He's cured many townsfolk
of lingering illness.

287
00:13:26,020 --> 00:13:27,020
He's compassionate

288
00:13:27,020 --> 00:13:28,540
and deeply admired by the people.

289
00:13:28,688 --> 00:13:30,300
No one has heard anything suspicious.

290
00:13:30,580 --> 00:13:33,060
Magistrate Wu, compile the movements
of the three victims

291
00:13:33,060 --> 00:13:34,580
over the past six months

292
00:13:34,620 --> 00:13:36,020
and deliver the report to me.

293
00:13:36,740 --> 00:13:38,780
Find out what connections they had

294
00:13:39,140 --> 00:13:40,740
and what happened to them recently.

295
00:13:41,020 --> 00:13:42,620
Do not overlook a single detail.

296
00:13:42,740 --> 00:13:43,340
Yes, sir.

297
00:13:53,700 --> 00:13:54,940
It's raining again.

298
00:13:55,580 --> 00:13:56,180
Di,

299
00:13:56,500 --> 00:13:58,740
are you worried
the murderer will strike again?

300
00:13:58,740 --> 00:14:00,380
I have a bad feeling.

301
00:14:00,630 --> 00:14:02,900
The murderer won't stop here.

302
00:14:03,250 --> 00:14:05,900
Such brutal murders.

303
00:14:06,066 --> 00:14:06,950
He must've suffered

304
00:14:06,960 --> 00:14:08,980
a devastating blow himself.

305
00:14:09,220 --> 00:14:10,860
Each time he kills,

306
00:14:11,500 --> 00:14:13,780
he gains a brief sense
of release and satisfaction.

307
00:14:13,980 --> 00:14:14,620
That's why

308
00:14:14,660 --> 00:14:16,860
the time of his killings
follows a pattern.

309
00:14:16,970 --> 00:14:18,900
What worries me
is that some external trigger

310
00:14:18,940 --> 00:14:20,820
may push him to kill again even sooner.

311
00:14:25,244 --> 00:14:26,220
Split into two teams.

312
00:14:26,610 --> 00:14:28,380
Search the woods
around Mingguang Temple.

313
00:14:28,410 --> 00:14:30,250
Do not let a single
suspicious person escape.

314
00:14:30,260 --> 00:14:31,200
- Yes, sir.
- Yes, sir.

315
00:14:31,810 --> 00:14:34,020
Ahead on the slope of West Mountain
is Mingguang Temple.

316
00:14:34,020 --> 00:14:35,066
Di, it's late Xu hour now.

317
00:14:35,070 --> 00:14:36,820
The rain is heavy,
and the roads are slippery.

318
00:14:36,820 --> 00:14:38,420
Maybe we can go tomorrow.

319
00:14:38,460 --> 00:14:40,180
Yes, Master. The temple is sacred ground.

320
00:14:40,220 --> 00:14:41,620
I don't think the murderer

321
00:14:41,940 --> 00:14:43,180
would dare kill there.

322
00:14:44,180 --> 00:14:45,180
This heavy rain

323
00:14:45,320 --> 00:14:46,900
unnerves me.

324
00:14:47,300 --> 00:14:48,220
Sir!

325
00:14:50,300 --> 00:14:50,740
Sir!

326
00:14:50,940 --> 00:14:52,060
Someone has come to report

327
00:14:52,060 --> 00:14:53,020
a missing lady!

328
00:14:53,460 --> 00:14:54,270
Sir,

329
00:14:54,340 --> 00:14:56,580
my daughter Shuitao left home
around the You hour

330
00:14:56,610 --> 00:14:58,300
and has yet to return.

331
00:14:58,300 --> 00:14:59,020
Sir!

332
00:14:59,180 --> 00:15:00,060
Mister,

333
00:15:00,220 --> 00:15:01,540
where did your daughter go?

334
00:15:01,580 --> 00:15:02,540
I don't know.

335
00:15:02,540 --> 00:15:03,670
She didn't tell me.

336
00:15:03,730 --> 00:15:05,980
Please save my daughter, sir!

337
00:15:06,577 --> 00:15:07,660
Calm yourself, Mister.

338
00:15:07,820 --> 00:15:08,820
Calm down.

339
00:15:09,420 --> 00:15:11,340
Perhaps your daughter
went to visit a friend.

340
00:15:12,020 --> 00:15:12,860
My daughter

341
00:15:13,040 --> 00:15:14,780
was wearing red.

342
00:16:04,500 --> 00:16:05,220
Lin,

343
00:16:05,370 --> 00:16:06,780
let's split up.

344
00:16:06,780 --> 00:16:07,820
If anything happens,

345
00:16:07,820 --> 00:16:08,888
signal with the whistle.

346
00:16:10,820 --> 00:16:11,180
Alright.

347
00:16:11,340 --> 00:16:11,780
Duan,

348
00:16:11,780 --> 00:16:12,820
be careful.

349
00:16:12,820 --> 00:16:13,660
Move out.

350
00:16:24,380 --> 00:16:27,420
(Main Hall)

351
00:16:36,020 --> 00:16:39,020
(Huiwu, Abbot of Mingguang Temple)

352
00:17:34,900 --> 00:17:36,020
(Preview of Next Episode)

353
00:17:45,260 --> 00:17:48,380
What was Sun Mao doing in the study?

354
00:17:48,860 --> 00:17:49,700
What secret

355
00:17:50,240 --> 00:17:52,860
is hidden here?

356
00:17:55,580 --> 00:17:57,060
Why is there a weiqi board here?

357
00:18:08,031 --> 00:18:09,611
♪Night covers the long streets♪

358
00:18:10,691 --> 00:18:12,401
♪The city remains silent♪

359
00:18:13,791 --> 00:18:15,381
♪Wind turns the old pages♪

360
00:18:15,641 --> 00:18:17,881
♪Words still left unspoken♪

361
00:18:19,281 --> 00:18:20,921
♪Bloodstains still hold their warmth♪

362
00:18:22,051 --> 00:18:24,521
♪Lamplight slowly tilts aside♪

363
00:18:25,141 --> 00:18:26,621
♪Who hides in the shadows♪

364
00:18:26,621 --> 00:18:29,761
♪Still circling around the truth?♪

365
00:18:30,381 --> 00:18:32,301
♪Love is born from desire♪

366
00:18:32,991 --> 00:18:35,121
♪Hatred rises out of greed♪

367
00:18:36,261 --> 00:18:37,921
♪One thought becomes a snare♪

368
00:18:37,921 --> 00:18:41,221
♪A lifetime trapped within♪

369
00:18:42,671 --> 00:18:43,991
♪Someone once warned me♪

370
00:18:43,991 --> 00:18:45,511
♪To stop upon this shore♪

371
00:18:45,511 --> 00:18:46,831
♪But sunlight burns too fiercely♪

372
00:18:46,831 --> 00:18:48,321
♪Fragile eyes break too easily♪

373
00:18:48,321 --> 00:18:49,441
♪If one thought retreats♪

374
00:18:49,441 --> 00:18:50,741
♪Then all things rest in peace♪

375
00:18:50,741 --> 00:18:52,081
♪But in this world♪

376
00:18:52,081 --> 00:18:54,481
♪Who will make the final judgment?♪

377
00:18:56,311 --> 00:18:59,121
♪If truth is cold as a frosted blade♪

378
00:18:59,121 --> 00:19:00,591
♪Still I walk ahead♪

379
00:19:00,821 --> 00:19:02,041
♪Let it pierce through♪

380
00:19:02,041 --> 00:19:06,781
♪The illusions before my eyes♪

381
00:19:06,781 --> 00:19:09,021
♪Layer upon layer of deception♪

382
00:19:09,021 --> 00:19:10,421
♪Covering every heart♪

383
00:19:10,421 --> 00:19:11,611
♪How many people♪

384
00:19:11,871 --> 00:19:13,241
♪Weave their own cocoon♪

385
00:19:13,241 --> 00:19:15,451
♪Yet call it♪

386
00:19:15,651 --> 00:19:16,991
♪Fate?♪

387
00:19:17,351 --> 00:19:18,531
♪Life and death♪

388
00:19:18,531 --> 00:19:19,791
♪Balanced on a single line♪

389
00:19:20,141 --> 00:19:21,311
♪Light and shadow♪

390
00:19:21,311 --> 00:19:22,571
♪Hanging side by side♪

391
00:19:22,571 --> 00:19:24,051
♪Goodness is not absolute♪

392
00:19:24,051 --> 00:19:25,461
♪Nor is evil ever complete♪

393
00:19:25,461 --> 00:19:27,001
♪In the end, it is only♪

394
00:19:27,001 --> 00:19:28,381
♪A single misguided thought♪

395
00:19:28,381 --> 00:19:29,941
♪If unveiling the truth♪

396
00:19:29,941 --> 00:19:31,281
♪Requires abandoning tenderness♪

397
00:19:31,281 --> 00:19:32,451
♪Then this answer♪

398
00:19:32,451 --> 00:19:33,811
♪Can it still remain true?♪

399
00:19:33,811 --> 00:19:35,211
♪When love and law♪

400
00:19:35,211 --> 00:19:36,691
♪Stand against each other in silence♪

401
00:19:36,691 --> 00:19:38,091
♪Which figure before me♪

402
00:19:38,091 --> 00:19:45,291
♪Am I meant to believe?♪

403
00:19:45,291 --> 00:19:48,021
♪If truth is cold as a frosted blade♪

404
00:19:48,021 --> 00:19:49,611
♪Still I walk ahead♪

405
00:19:49,611 --> 00:19:50,851
♪Not for fame or glory♪

406
00:19:50,851 --> 00:19:55,721
♪Nor caring who wins or loses♪

407
00:19:55,721 --> 00:19:57,531
♪Human nature is clouded♪

408
00:19:57,531 --> 00:19:59,251
♪Yet still reflects the stars♪

409
00:19:59,251 --> 00:20:00,721
♪Though this world♪

410
00:20:00,721 --> 00:20:02,091
♪Is filled with mud and mire♪

411
00:20:02,091 --> 00:20:04,341
♪There is still a light♪

412
00:20:04,341 --> 00:20:07,301
♪Worth pursuing♪

413
00:20:07,301 --> 00:20:09,121
♪Every case has its ending♪

414
00:20:09,121 --> 00:20:10,381
♪But night does not always fade♪

415
00:20:10,651 --> 00:20:12,031
♪The wind stops, the pages close♪

416
00:20:12,031 --> 00:20:13,251
♪Yet hearts remain unsettled♪

417
00:20:13,521 --> 00:20:14,601
♪If justice stands♪

418
00:20:14,601 --> 00:20:15,851
♪Without mercy beside it♪

419
00:20:15,851 --> 00:20:17,651
♪Then how is it♪

420
00:20:17,651 --> 00:20:27,211
♪Any different from a blade?♪

421
00:20:27,211 --> 00:20:30,401
♪If truth is cold as a frosted blade♪

422
00:20:30,401 --> 00:20:31,881
♪Still I walk ahead♪

423
00:20:31,881 --> 00:20:33,271
♪Even if the world♪

424
00:20:33,271 --> 00:20:38,001
♪Refuses to answer♪

425
00:20:38,001 --> 00:20:39,961
♪When every hidden truth♪

426
00:20:39,961 --> 00:20:41,671
♪Finally reveals itself♪

427
00:20:41,671 --> 00:20:43,031
♪I only wish♪

428
00:20:43,031 --> 00:20:44,511
♪To hold on♪

429
00:20:44,511 --> 00:20:49,251
♪Within the darkness♪

430
00:20:49,251 --> 00:20:51,251
♪To the heart♪
